spec_data.Name: konqueror-mldonkey-ed2k-support
spec_data.Description:
This package contains tool which gives you an easy way to add an ed2k-link
(like ed2k://|file|filename.exe|21352658|72b0b287cab7d875ccc1d89ebe910b9g|)
with a single click to your mldonkey download queue.
You need to edit /etc/sysconfig/mldonkey_submit
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:39:13 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Easy way to download a ed2k-link from Konqueror
